
Notify All

About
=====

Notifications for GNOME Desktop using libnotify to show updates from Twitter, GMail, Facebook or any RSS and Atom feed

* Display notifications with libnotify
* Show new messages from GMail usign GMail Atom feed
* Show status updates from Twitter using Twitter API
* Show notifications from Facebook notification feed
* Show news from RSS and Atom feeds
* Written in Python ;)


Author
======

Pablo Seminario
<pabluk@gmail.com>


Usage
=====

1. install dependencies
1.1 Ubuntu
    sudo aptitude install python-notify python-feedparser python-twitter
1.2 Arch Linux
    sudo pacman -S python-notify python-feedparser python-twitter
2. run on a terminal
    ./notifyall
   and press Ctrl+C to exit
3. edit user, password and additionals labels in ~/.notifyall/notifyall.cfg


